        Labs UI is an <a href="https://emberjs.com/">Ember.js</a> addon containing common components and design patterns used across <a href="https://planninglabs.nyc/">NYC Planning Labs</a> digital products, incorporating styles from our <a href="https://nyc-planning-style-guide.netlify.com/">Digital Style Guide</a>.
      </p>
