        The NYC Planning Digital Style Guide is built with <a href="https://foundation.zurb.com/sites/docs/">Foundation for Sites</a>. Consult the <a href="https://foundation.zurb.com/sites/docs/">Foundation docs</a> for features not covered in the style guide's docs. Note: Labs UI only consumes styles from the style guide/Foundation, it not its JavaScript.
